WEBVTT

00:01.843 --> 00:04.511
(wolf howls)

00:04.546 --> 00:06.546
(inhaling, exhaling)

00:09.151 --> 00:10.383
Don't, don't, don't...
(laughing)

00:10.419 --> 00:11.384
Don't, don't!

00:11.420 --> 00:12.786
Don't do that, don't do it!

00:12.821 --> 00:14.754
Don't do that, you tickle me.

00:14.790 --> 00:17.023
You made the spray paint
come out of my nose.

00:17.059 --> 00:18.892
What, do I have
paint on my face?

00:18.927 --> 00:21.394
Dude, look at the moon!

00:21.430 --> 00:23.964
Oh, whoa...

00:27.336 --> 00:28.601
What?

00:28.637 --> 00:30.270
When you see a moon like that,

00:30.305 --> 00:31.438
do you ever think...

00:31.473 --> 00:34.240
life is so amazing

00:34.276 --> 00:36.843
and maybe we
shouldn't waste it

00:36.878 --> 00:39.079
by just getting
high all the time?

00:39.114 --> 00:40.847
No.

00:40.882 --> 00:43.950
I think about how
I wish I were a werewolf.

00:43.986 --> 00:46.286
What would you do
if you were a werewolf?

00:46.321 --> 00:47.921
Get high all the time.

00:47.956 --> 00:50.056
(man panting, yelling)

00:50.092 --> 00:52.092
- (footsteps approaching)
- What's that?

00:52.127 --> 00:53.693
MAN:
Aah!

00:53.729 --> 00:54.828
Where'd that come from?

00:54.863 --> 00:57.564
(growling, man screaming)

00:59.001 --> 01:00.066
(roaring)

01:00.102 --> 01:01.167
(screaming)

01:01.203 --> 01:02.602
(roars)

01:05.507 --> 01:07.407
Did that just happen?

01:07.442 --> 01:09.576
(man grunts)

01:09.611 --> 01:11.344
Hey. Hey, hey.

01:11.380 --> 01:13.980
Whoa, dude.
Dude, are you okay?

01:14.016 --> 01:15.749
Yeah, I think so.

01:15.784 --> 01:17.183
Dude, are you okay?

01:17.219 --> 01:19.819
Dude, he just said
that he was.

01:19.855 --> 01:21.287
No, not this dude.

01:21.323 --> 01:24.290
<i>This</i> dude.

01:25.494 --> 01:27.160
Whoa, dude.

01:32.768 --> 01:33.867
I don't think that...

01:33.902 --> 01:35.935
that dude's okay.

